gettext-perl: gettext-perl (Internationalization for Perl)
gettext-perl:
gettext-perl: This is a perl5 module quickly written to gain access to the C 
gettext-perl: library functions for internatialization using an object oriented 
gettext-perl: interface suitable to native Perl programs. This library is free
gettext-perl: software; you may distribute under the terms of either the GNU 
gettext-perl: General Public License.
gettext-perl: 
gettext-perl: Locale::gettext was written by Phillip Vandry <vandry@tzone.org>
